14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 26 O.S. 2021, Section 3-101, as
16 amended by Section 2, Chapter 329, O.S.L. 2023 (26 O.S. Supp. 2024,
17 Section 3-101), is amended to read as follows:
18 Section 3-101. A. No election required to be conducted by any
19 county election board shall be scheduled for a day other than
20 Tuesday.
21 B. Except as otherwise provided by law, no regular or special
22 election to fill an elective office for any purpose shall be held by
23 any county, school district, technology center school district,
